306
00:16:41,346 --> 00:16:42,646
It's a ghost!

307
00:16:42,646 --> 00:16:46,746
I'm sure the ghost of that student called Hosaka took it there!

308
00:16:46,746 --> 00:16:48,446
It's possible.

309
00:16:48,446 --> 00:16:50,246
Because ghosts don't have legs.

310
00:16:50,246 --> 00:16:52,546
Come on, all of you...

311
00:16:52,546 --> 00:16:54,646
Hey.

312
00:16:54,646 --> 00:16:57,646
