329
00:17:47,646 --> 00:17:52,846
This ghost scare is his curse!

330
00:17:54,446 --> 00:17:58,046
By chance, do you happen to know this student called Hosaka?

331
00:17:59,046 --> 00:18:00,046
Yeah.

332
00:18:00,046 --> 00:18:02,746
