334
00:18:07,046 --> 00:18:08,446
Back then...

335
00:18:08,446 --> 00:18:11,046
Don't tell me you were there when this happened?

336
00:18:12,746 --> 00:18:14,546
Just as I thought.

337
00:18:14,546 --> 00:18:16,946
Back then when the accident occurred, this student...

338
00:18:17,946 --> 00:18:20,646
-Please leave. -What?

339
00:18:20,646 --> 00:18:24,146
The teacher was nice enough to let me use this art room all by myself

340
00:18:24,146 --> 00:18:27,846
so that I would be able to complete my piece for the contest.

341
00:18:27,846 --> 00:18:29,146
Go on, quickly!

342
00:18:29,146 --> 00:18:32,046
I don't want to waste any time!

343
00:18:32,046 --> 00:18:33,446
Okay.

344
00:18:43,846 --> 00:18:48,346
Should we let Kazumi know that the desk was out on campus, too?

345
00:18:48,346 --> 00:18:49,746
Okay.

346
00:18:52,046 --> 00:18:53,846
Something's shining.

347
00:18:53,846 --> 00:18:55,346
What is it?

348
00:18:59,046 --> 00:19:00,146
Wax?

349
00:19:00,146 --> 00:19:02,746
What's the matter, Conan?

350
00:19:02,746 --> 00:19:06,746
You said that the bottom of the stairs was soaked with water,

351
00:19:06,746 --> 00:19:08,446
