352
00:19:08,446 --> 00:19:12,746
Right! The entire floor!

353
00:19:12,746 --> 00:19:17,346
The tears of the curse of the student named Hosaka that died here.

354
00:19:17,346 --> 00:19:19,746
Who found that?

355
00:19:19,746 --> 00:19:22,146
I heard that it was someone from the art club

356
00:19:22,146 --> 00:19:23,646
